data.description: If you've been searching for the perfect country setup at an affordable price, the search stops HERE! Approaching this 4 bedroom 2.5 bath craftsman style pool home on approximately one acre, you will notice the sprawling yard completely fenced with metal fencing and solar powered gate for privacy. You will also notice several chicken coops, a small pond, 20x20 pole barn, 20x30 outbuilding, 12x24 storage shed, privacy fenced in pool area, and so much more! Entering the home, you will step into a wide open floor plan with soaring ceilings and immediately be drawn to the beautifully renovated kitchen with custom cabinetry, stainless appliances, quartz countertops, and convenience to the spacious laundry room that leads out to the garage. The laundry room here features a heated fan, deep washing sink, many cabinets for storage, and a butcher block style countertop. Back through the kitchen, we have our dining area open/convenient to the kitchen and screened in back porch for easy entertaining! This home features a split floor plan with 3 bedrooms on one side of the house and master bedroom on the opposite side of the home. Some updates include LVP flooring, fresh paint, and beautifully updated lighting throughout. All measurements approximate. Buyer to verify if important. Schedule your showing to see this immaculate home today!
